 Ask if she wants to get married. If she says yes, wait three days, if she says no, ask again in one day. If she says yes the second time, wait one year, if she says no, ask again in one day. If she says yes the third time, wait two years, if she says no the third time, wait five years. If she says yes the fourth time, wait ten years, if she said no the fourth time, wait twenty years.
